      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bet pa ikkatru to Zeltu/ ko tas KUNGS juhfu Deews jums pawehft buhs jums statgaht/ ka juhs dsihwojat/ un jums lab- bi klahjahs/ un ilgi dsihwojat tai Semmê / ko juhs eemantofeet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "N schee irr tee Bausli/tee Vikkuni/un tahs Teefas/ ko tas KUNGS juhfu Deews pawehlejs irr jums mah- zihf / ka juhs tohs darrat tai Semmê / us kurren juhs eetat winnu eemantoht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ka tu to KUNGU tawu Deewu bibstees / un turri wiffus winna Likkumus / un winna Bauslus/ ko es tew pawehftu / tu un taws Behrns/ un tawi Behr- nu Behrni / wiffâs tawas Dsih- wibas Deenâs/ ka tu ilgi dsihwo.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Klaufsajs tad Israels / un nemm wehrâ / ka tu tohs darrt/ ka tew labbi klahjahs/ un ka juhs lohti wairoti tohpat / itt ka tas KUNGS tawu Tehwu Deews tew runnajs irr/ eekfch tahsSem- mes / kas ar Peenu un Meddu teke.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Klaufsajs Israels / tas KUNGS mühju Deews / tas KUNGS/ irr weens.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tew buhs to KUNGU tawu Deewu mihleht/ no wiffas tawas Sirđs / un no wiffas ta- was Dwehfeles/ un no wiffa ta- wa Spehka.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un schee Wahrdi/ko es teiw schodeen pawehftu / laid tew pee Sirđs eet.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tew buhs tohs taweem Behrneem peefohdinaht / un no teem runnaht tawa Namma feh dedams / un pa Zeltu eedams/ gulledams / un augfchamzelda- mees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tew buhs tohs par Sih- mi us tawu Rohku feet / un teem buhs par Beeminnefchanas-Sih- mi buht starp tawahm Azzim.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tew buhs tohs us tawa Namma Stendexeem/ un us ta- wahm Wahrtim rakstiht.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Kad nu tas KUNGS taws Deews tew eeweddihs tai Semmê/ ko wiſch taweem Teh- weem Ahbradnam / Jhsaäkam un Jehkabam sivehrejs irr tew doht/ leelus un labbus Pilstah- tus/ ko tu ne effi ustaifsigs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un Nammus wiffa Lab- buma pilnus / ko tu ne effi pil- dijs/ un iszirstas Akkas/ ko tu ne effi iszirtis/ Wihna-Dahrsus un Etjes-Rohku Dahrsus/ ko tu ne effi dehsiijs/ ka tew irr ja-ehd/ un japee-ehd.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tad fargajs / ka tu to KUNGU ne aisminrsti/ ka tew no Egiptes-Semmês no ta Wehr- gu-Namma isweddis irr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tew buhs to KUNGU tawu\n"
    }
  ],
